INSERT INTO MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1 SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Q.SK_MUNICIPIO)+ Q.SK_ETAPA AS SK_ETAPA, Q.SK_MUNICIPIO AS SK_MUNICIPIO, Q.ETAPA, Q.META_X_ETAPA AS META_ETAPA, Q.TMCODE, Q.ESTADO, Q.FEC_ESTADO, SYSDATE FEC_CARGA, SYSDATE FEC_ACTUALIZA FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT ID_MAXIMO.SK_ETAPA AS SK_ETAPA, TRIM(ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.ETAPA) ETAPA, ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.SK_MUNICIPIO SK_MUNICIPIO, ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.ESTADO, ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.META_X_ETAPA, ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.FEC_ESTADO, ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.TMCODE FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT ETAPA AS ETAPA ,T1.TMCODE AS TMCODE ,T2.SK_MUNICIPIO AS SK_MUNICIPIO ,T1.ESTADO AS ESTADO ,T1.FEC_ESTADO AS FEC_ESTADO ,T1.META_X_ETAPA AS META_X_ETAPA ,T1.DANE AS DANE FROM MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TMP_TB T1 LEFT JOIN TBL_DIM_MUNICIPIOS_DANE_T1 T2 ON cast(regexp_replace(T1.DANE, '[^0-9]+', '') as number)=T2.COD_MUNICIPIO -- WHERE ROWNUM =1 WHERE (T2.TIP_CENTRO_POBLADO = 'CABECERA MUNICIPAL (CM)' OR T2.TIP_CENTRO_POBLADO = 'NO APLICA') GROUP BY ETAPA ,TMCODE ,SK_MUNICIPIO ,ESTADO ,FEC_ESTADO ,META_X_ETAPA ,T1.DANE )ESTADO_PIN_PAGO LEFT JOIN MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TMP_TB TMP_ESTADO ON TMP_ESTADO.ETAPA = ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.ETAPA AND TMP_ESTADO.TMCODE= ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.TMCODE AND TMP_ESTADO.DANE= ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.DANE AND TMP_ESTADO.META_X_ETAPA= ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.META_X_ETAPA INNER JOIN (SELECT NVL(MAX(SK_ETAPA), 0) SK_ETAPA FROM MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1 WHERE SK_ETAPA > 0 ) ID_MAXIMO ON 1 = 1 LEFT JOIN MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1 TMP_PINES ON TRIM(ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.ETAPA) = TMP_PINES.ETAPA AND TMP_ESTADO.TMCODE= TMP_PINES.TMCODE --AND TMP_ESTADO.SK_MUNICIPIO= TMP_PINES.SK_MUNICIPIO AND TMP_ESTADO.META_X_ETAPA= TMP_PINES.META_ETAPA WHERE TMP_PINES.SK_ETAPA IS NULL AND (TRIM(ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.TMCODE) IS NOT NULL OR TRIM(ESTADO_PIN_PAGO.TMCODE) <> '') ) Q

MERGE INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_PLAN_ENTREGA_TB_PR") ?> T1 USING (SELECT A.SK_MUNICIPIO ,A.TMCODE ,A.ETAPA ,A.NUM_DOC ,B.SK_ETAPA FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.SK_MUNICIPIO_M ELSE T3.SK_MUNICIPIO END AS SK_MUNICIPIO ,REPLACE (REPLACE (REPLACE (T2.TMCODE, CHR (10), ''), CHR (13), ''),'','')TMCODE ,T3.META AS ETAPA ,T2.NUM_DOC FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_PLAN_ENTREGA_TB_PR") ?> T1 JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB_PR") ?> T2 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = T2.NUM_DOC) JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB_PR") ?> T3 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T3.NUM_DOC END) AND T2.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T3.NUM_DOC END)) WHERE T3.SK_ETAPA = -1)A JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1") ?> B ON (A.SK_MUNICIPIO = B.SK_MUNICIPIO AND REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(A.TMCODE,CHR (10),''),CHR(13),''),'','') = REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(B.TMCODE,CHR(10),''),CHR (13), ''),'','') AND A.ETAPA = B.ETAPA) GROUP BY A.SK_MUNICIPIO ,A.TMCODE ,A.ETAPA ,A.NUM_DOC ,B.SK_ETAPA) T2 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = T2.NUM_DOC) WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET T1.SK_ETAPA = T2.SK_ETAPA

MERGE INTO <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB_PR") ?> T1 USING (SELECT A.SK_MUNICIPIO ,A.TMCODE ,A.ETAPA ,A.NUM_DOC ,B.SK_ETAPA FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.SK_MUNICIPIO_M ELSE T3.SK_MUNICIPIO END AS SK_MUNICIPIO ,REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(T2.TMCODE,CHR (10),''),CHR (13),''),'','')TMCODE ,T1.ETAPA ,T2.NUM_DOC FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INF_PLAN_ENTREGA_TMP_TB") ?> T1 JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_DUPLAS_TB_PR") ?> T2 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = T2.NUM_DOC) JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_INFO_BASE_BENEFI_TB_PR") ?> T3 ON (T1.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T3.NUM_DOC END) AND T2.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T3.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T3.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T3.NUM_DOC END)))A JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("MINTIC_ESTADO_ETAPA_DIM_TB_T1") ?> B ON (A.SK_MUNICIPIO = B.SK_MUNICIPIO AND REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(A.TMCODE,CHR(10),''),CHR (13),''),'','') = REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(B.TMCODE,CHR(10),''),CHR(13),''),'','') AND A.ETAPA = B.ETAPA) GROUP BY A.SK_MUNICIPIO ,A.TMCODE ,A.ETAPA ,A.NUM_DOC ,B.SK_ETAPA) T2 ON (T2.NUM_DOC = (CASE WHEN T1.SK_CATEG_BENEF = 1 THEN T1.NUM_IDENT_MENOR ELSE T1.NUM_DOC END)) WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET T1.META = T2.ETAPA WHERE T1.META = -1
